===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|sise|sise, syse|regulation, control, limit}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|cise|}}, {{m|fro|sise|}}, aphetism of ''[[assise]]'' "assize". Displaced native {{etyl|enm|-}} {{m|enm|grete|grete, grette|size}} (from {{etyl|ang|-}} {{m|ang|grietu|grīetu, grȳtu|size, greatness}}).

